## ❌ Mistake #4: File in Wrong Directory

**Frequency:** Common
**Last Occurrence:** -

### Problem
```
src/components/auth/LoginForm.tsx  // ❌ Not feature-based
src/utils/auth/helper.ts           // ❌ Not in lib/
```

### Solution
```
src/features/auth/components/LoginForm.tsx  // ✅ Feature-based
src/lib/utils/auth/helper.ts                // ✅ Shared utilities
```

**Detection Command:**
```bash
# Find files outside feature structure
find src -name "*.tsx" -o -name "*.ts" | \
  grep -v "node_modules" | \
  grep -v "features/.*/\(api\|components\|hooks\|types\)" | \
  grep -v "lib/" | \
  grep -v "config/"
```

