## ❌ Mistake #5: Direct Database Access in Client Component

**Frequency:** Rare (compile error)
**Last Occurrence:** -

### Problem
```tsx
"use client"
import { prisma } from '@/lib/db'

export function UserList() {
  const users = await prisma.user.findMany()  // ❌ Can't run in browser!
  return <ul>...</ul>
}
```

### Error Message
```
Error: Module not found: Can't resolve 'prisma/client'
Prisma can only run on the server.
```

### Solution
Option 1: Convert to Server Component
```tsx
// Remove "use client"
export default async function UserList() {
  const users = await prisma.user.findMany()
  return <ul>...</ul>
}
```

Option 2: Use API route
```tsx
"use client"
export function UserList() {
  const { data } = useSWR('/api/users', fetcher)
  return <ul>...</ul>
}
```

