## ❌ Mistake #6: Not Using TypeScript Strict Mode

**Frequency:** Setup issue
**Last Occurrence:** -

### Problem
```json
// tsconfig.json
{
  "compilerOptions": {
    "strict": false  // ❌ Missing type safety
  }
}
```

### Solution
```json
// tsconfig.json
{
  "compilerOptions": {
    "strict": true,  // ✅ Enable all strict checks
    "noUncheckedIndexedAccess": true,
    "noImplicitReturns": true
  }
}
```

